Package: catool
Type: Package
Title: Compensation Analysis Tool for Instructor Overload Pay
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Dawit", "Aberra", email = "dawit3000@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Calculates fair and transparent overload compensation for college instructors 
    based on institutional policies, teaching load limits, and enrollment thresholds. 
    The package identifies qualified credit hours above regular load, applies enrollment-based 
    proration where appropriate, and produces spreadsheet-ready, human-readable summary tables 
    for instructors and full schedules. Includes functions for flexible filtering, policy customization, 
    and output suitable for audits and administrative reporting.
